===2015 Awards=== In 2015, [[Technobabylon]] won the most awards of all the nominees, taking home 9. ''Troll Song: Verse One - Completely Stoned'' won the Best Demo Awards at the AGS Awards 2015. This was the second time Troll Song has won an AGS Award for ''Best Tech Demo'', with the original tech demo claiming the prize at the 2013 AGS Awards.<ref>[http://www.troll-song.com/2016/06/troll-song-wins-best-demo-at-ags-awards.html Troll Song wins AGS Award 2015]</ref> The '''Lifetime Achievement Award''' was awarded to indie developer Peder Johnsen ''"for his services with AGS archives, hosting and many other contributions over the years"''.
