===2014 Awards=== In 2014, the [[Role-playing video game|RPG]] game ''Quest for Infamy'' won in 4 categories including ''Best Gameplay'' and ''Best Puzzles''. After the award ceremony the developers of Quest for Infamy announced they'd making a prequel and a sequel to the game.<ref>[https://www.gamingonlinux.com/articles/developer-infamous-%20quests-has-announced-two-new-pointandclick-adventures-to-be-%20released-this-year.5169 Developer Infamous Quests Has Announced Two New Point-And-Click Adventures] gamingonlinux.com</ref>
